      • identify

        public HashMap<HashSet<IsotopeDistribution>,Double> identify(IdealMassSpectrum spectrum)
        identify an isotope distribution as belonging to a molecule or a set of molecules.
        Parameters:
        spectrum - the mass spectrum to identify
        Returns:
        a map of results to the algorithms degree of belief of those results. each result is in the form of a set of isotope distributions which are properly qualified with their associated molecules.
